<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.8">
<l>vañci maruṅku liṭainōva maṇantu niṉṟa kaṉavakatteṉ</l>
<l>neñcu niṟaiyak kaikūppi niṉṟār niṉṟa vūrpōlum</l>
<l>pañci yaṉṉa mellaṭinaṟ pāvai mārka ḷāṭakattiṉ</l>
<l>añci lampi ṉārppōvā vaṇiyār vīti yaḻuntūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city where stands the one who, in a dream in which [we] kept embracing,</l>
<l>So that my vañci [creeper-like] waist ached [and] so my heart was full,</l>
<l rend="indent">stayed joining his hands,</l>
<l>It seems is Aḻuntūr with beautiful streets where never ceases the sound</l>
<l>Of pretty, golden ankle bells of lovely maidens with feet as soft as cotton.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
